Quickstrike followed quickly by Double Punch. He entered the base with 
relief. He looked up at the Predacon with the pain on his claws. "Get 'er t' 
th' CR chambers. Ah need some repairs too. Make sure Transulas don't get 
'er. Ah needs t' find somethin' out 'bout 'er." He skittered off to the CR 
room.
